### Get all users (Public, no auth required)
GET http://localhost:5249/users
Accept: application/json

###

### Get user by ID (Public, no auth required)
GET http://localhost:5249/users/2
Accept: application/json

###

### Create user (Protected, missing token)
POST http://localhost:5249/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jana",
  "email": "jana@example.com"
}

###

### Create user (Protected, with valid token)
POST http://localhost:5249/users
Authorization: Bearer my-secret-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jana",
  "email": "jana@example.com"
}

###

### Create user (Protected, with invalid token)
POST http://localhost:5249/users
Authorization: Bearer wrong-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jana",
  "email": "jana@example.com"
}

###

### Create user (Protected, with validation error)
POST http://localhost:5249/users
